RST Efficiency Summary Data

efficiency_summary.Rd

Dataset containing summarized efficiency monitoring data for all SR JPE tribuatary and mainstem monitoring programs

efficiency_summary

Format

  • date_released: Date that efficiency trial release occurs (format - %Y-%m-%d)

  • release_id: The unique identifier for each release trial

  • stream: Which stream the RST is located on

  • site: Site name

  • subsite: Name of trap

  • site_group: Site group, used to seperate traps within the same stream that have unique environmental conditions.

  • number_released: Count of fish released

  • number_recaptured: Count of fish recaptured in RST on a specific recapture date, when NA trap is not fished

  • run: Run of fish released

  • life_stage: Lifestage of fish released

  • origin: Fish origin (natural, hatchery, mixed, unknown, not recorded, or NA)

Source

Raw datasets and original documentation of data processing and QC process can be found for each stream using the links below. Data is combined here

  • Battle Creek: Data on EDI, Original Data Exploration Script. Additional data exploration scripts are located in GitHub.

  • Butte Creek: Data on EDI, Original Data Exploration Script. Additional data exploration scripts are located in GitHub.

  • Clear Creek: Data on EDI, Original Data Exploration Script. Additional data exploration scripts are located in GitHub.

  • Deer Creek: Data on EDI

  • Feather River: Data on EDI, Original Data Exploration Script. Additional data exploration scripts are located in GitHub.

  • Mill Creek: Data on EDI

    • Knights Landing: Data on EDI, Original Data Exploration Script. Additional data exploration scripts are located in GitHub.

    • Tisdale: Data on EDI, Original Data Exploration Script. Additional data exploration scripts are located in GitHub.

    • Delta Entry: Data on EDI.

  • Yuba River: Data on EDI, Original Data Exploration Script. Additional data exploration scripts are located in GitHub.
